PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by the Province of ALBERTA of its statutory power to acquire some 3.162 hectares of land on Makaoo Indian Reserve No. 120, for highways and public utility purposes, and (b) in lieu thereof, authorizing the transfer to the Province of administration and control over the lands in question for so long as they are required for those purposes.
